<script>
  (function() {
    !function (f, b, e, v, n, t, s) {
      if (f.fbq)
        return;n = f.fbq = function () {
          n.callMethod ?
            n.callMethod.apply(n, arguments) : n.queue.push(arguments)
        };
      if (!f._fbq)
        f._fbq = n;
      n.push = n;
      n.loaded = !0;
      n.version = '2.0';
      n.queue = [];
      t = b.createElement(e);

      s.parentNode.insertBefore(t, s)
    }(window,
      document, 'script', 'https://connect.facebook.net/en_US/fbevents.js');

      utm_source: {{utmSource}},

</script>

<script>
  (function() {
    fbq('trackCustom', '{{Event}}', {
      //event
      event_category: {{eventCategory}},
      event_action: {{eventAction}},
      event_label: {{eventLabel}},
      event_value: {{eventValue}},
      //UTM tags
      utm_source: {{utmSource}},
      utm_medium: {{utmMedium}},
      utm_campaign: {{utmCampaign}},
      utm_term: {{utmTerm}},
      utm_content: {{utmContent}},
      //metrics
      active_time: {{activeTime}},
      referrer: document.referrer,
      userAgent: navigator.userAgent,
      language: navigator.language
    });
  })();
</script>

<script>
  (function () {

    if ('{{fbEvent}}' === 'ViewContent') {
      fbq('track', '{{fbEvent}}', {
        content_category: {{eventCategory}},
        content_ids: {{eventAction}},
        content_name: {{eventValue}},
        content_label: {{eventLabel}},
        content_type: {{contentType}},
        value: {{value}},
        currency: {{currency}},
        pdt_code: {{pdtCode}},
        content_transaction: {{contentTransaction}},
        content_finality: {{contentFinality}},
        realty_ref: {{realtyRef}},
        class_time: {{classTime}},
        referrer: document.referrer,
        userAgent: navigator.userAgent,
        language: navigator.language
      });
    }

    if ('{{fbEvent}}' === 'Search') {
      fbq('track', '{{fbEvent}}', {
        search_string: {{searchString}},
        referrer: document.referrer,
        userAgent: navigator.userAgent,
        language: navigator.language
      });
    }

    if ('{{fbEvent}}' === 'CompleteRegistration') {
      fbq('track', '{{fbEvent}}', {
        content_category: {{eventCategory}},
        content_name: {{eventAction}},
        status: {{eventLabel}},
        referrer: document.referrer,
        userAgent: navigator.userAgent,
        language: navigator.language
      });
    }

    //ECOMMERCE
    if ('{{fbEvent}}' === 'AddToCart') {
      fbq('track', '{{fbEvent}}', {
        content_category: {{eventCategory}},
        content_ids: {{eventAction}},
        content_type: {{contentType}},
        value: {{value}},
        currency: {{currency}},
        referrer: document.referrer,
        userAgent: navigator.userAgent,
        language: navigator.language
      });
    }

    if ('{{fbEvent}}' === 'InitiateCheckout') {
      fbq('track', '{{fbEvent}}', {
        content_category: {{eventCategory}},
        referrer: document.referrer,
        userAgent: navigator.userAgent,
        language: navigator.language
      });
    }

    if ('{{fbEvent}}' === 'AddPaymentInfo') {
      fbq('track', '{{fbEvent}}', {
        content_category: {{eventCategory}},
        referrer: document.referrer,
        userAgent: navigator.userAgent,
        language: navigator.language
      });
    }

    if ('{{fbEvent}}' === 'Purchase') {
      fbq('track', '{{fbEvent}}', {
        content_category: {{eventCategory}},
        content_ids: {{eventAction}},
        content_type: {{contentType}},
        value: {{value}},
        currency: {{currency}},
        referrer: document.referrer,
        userAgent: navigator.userAgent,
        language: navigator.language
      });
    }

    //EAD
    if ('{{fbEvent}}' === 'Lead') {
      fbq('track', '{{fbEvent}}', {
        content_category: {{eventCategory}},
        content_name: {{eventAction}},
        referrer: document.referrer,
        userAgent: navigator.userAgent,
        language: navigator.language
      });
    }

  })();
</script>

<script>
  if (typeof FB !== 'undefined'){
    FB.Event.subscribe('edge.create',
                       function(href) {
      dataLayer.push({
        'event': 'socialInt', 
        'socialNetwork': 'Facebook', 
        'socialAction': 'Like', 
        'socialTarget': href
      });
    }
                      );
  }
  
  //twitter
  if (typeof twttr !== 'undefined') {
    twttr.ready(function (twttr) {
      twttr.events.bind('click', clickEventToAnalytics);  
    });
  }
  function clickEventToAnalytics() {
    dataLayer.push({
      'event': 'socialInt', 
      'socialNetwork': 'Twitter', 
      'socialAction': 'tweet', 
      'socialTarget': window.location.href
    });
  }
</script>
